00:41:11,800 --> 00:41:13,039
Then she'll probably be home soon.

839
00:41:13,039 --> 00:41:13,599
Yes, yes, yes.

840
00:41:13,599 --> 00:41:14,559
I'll head back now.

841
00:41:14,679 --> 00:41:16,039
Then go home and check.

842
00:41:16,039 --> 00:41:16,760
You two get some rest.

843
00:41:16,760 --> 00:41:17,480
Alright, alright.

844
00:41:18,320 --> 00:41:19,559
Drive safely on your way home.

845
00:41:19,559 --> 00:41:20,119
Okay, Dad.

846
00:41:28,039 --> 00:41:28,880
Where's Tingting?

847
00:41:29,079 --> 00:41:30,119
How would I know?

848
00:41:30,199 --> 00:41:31,840
You—you don't know?

849
00:41:31,840 --> 00:41:33,159
You said she was at a class reunion.

850
00:41:33,159 --> 00:41:34,880
Aren't you just making up excuses for her?

851
00:41:34,880 --> 00:41:36,320
Enough, keep your voice down.

852
00:41:36,519 --> 00:41:38,239
She has a family and a child.

853
00:41:38,239 --> 00:41:39,679
Shut up, don't you know?

854
00:41:47,280 --> 00:41:48,000
You're back.

855
00:42:02,000 --> 00:42:02,920
Where did you go?

856
00:42:04,639 --> 00:42:05,400
Out to eat.

857
00:42:05,400 --> 00:42:06,199
With whom?

858
00:42:08,880 --> 00:42:09,599
Colleagues.

859
00:42:12,599 --> 00:42:13,559
Then why did your mom say

860
00:42:13,559 --> 00:42:15,119
you went to a class dinner?

861
00:42:18,159 --> 00:42:19,320
What do you mean?

862
00:42:20,000 --> 00:42:21,119
Are you checking up on me?

863
00:42:21,920 --> 00:42:23,119
Are you interrogating a criminal?

864
00:42:28,480 --> 00:42:30,679
No, I'm just worried about you.

865
00:42:32,119 --> 00:42:33,280
Where did you actually go?

866
00:42:35,320 --> 00:42:35,679
So what?

867
00:42:35,679 --> 00:42:36,719
From now on, whatever I do

868
00:42:36,719 --> 00:42:38,760
I have to report to you first, is that it?

869
00:42:40,480 --> 00:42:41,920
What's wrong with just telling me?

870
00:42:45,280 --> 00:42:46,400
When I was discharged from the hospital

871
00:42:46,480 --> 00:42:47,719
wasn't it you who said

872
00:42:48,119 --> 00:42:49,800
I could do whatever I wanted?

873
00:42:50,079 --> 00:42:51,599
That I should do whatever makes me happy?

874
00:42:52,840 --> 00:42:53,719
Besides,

875
00:42:54,599 --> 00:42:57,320
have you ever cared about what I do?
